		  <h2>At a Glance</h2>
		  <p>I am currently a freshman at Harvard College, and I recently graduated from Park Tudor School, a high school in Indianapolis. I enjoy doing computer science and math, and I have combined those interests in a few internships and research projects (which you can read about on the <%= link_to "Projects page", projects_path %>). I'm also interested in history and ballroom dancing, and I occasionally make <%= link_to "fractal art", fractal_link%> in my free time.</p>
